{"427240":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Cosmic Trip","steam_appid":427240,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"dlc":[640400,640401],"detailed_description":"<h1>Supports Valve Index (and Index Controllers)<\/h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/427240\/extras\/CosmicTripIndexSupport.jpg?t=1725382268\" \/><br><i>Cosmic Trip<\/i> fully supports the Valve Index HMD and the Valve Index Controllers.<\/p><br><h1>数字豪华版<\/h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/427240\/extras\/CT-deluxe-edition.jpg?t=1725382268\" \/><br><br>The Digital Deluxe edition includes the following:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Cosmic Trip<br><\/li><li> 50+ Page Art Book<br><\/li><li> Official Soundtrack<\/li><\/ul><\/p><br><h1>关于游戏<\/h1><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/427240\/extras\/mixed-reality.jpg?t=1725382268\" \/><br><br>你降落在了一个充满敌人的外星星球上。你必须建造、指挥你的太空机器人大军来采集资源、摧毁敌人并保护自己。<br><br>原生VR即时战略！Cosmic Trip让你用前所未有的视野感受即时战略的魅力。体验使用高科技武器摧毁敌人的快感，或打造出一支强大的机器人大军来保护你并采集资源。<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/427240\/extras\/friend.jpg?t=1725382268\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">游戏特色<\/h2><strong>直观的VR原生控制<\/strong><br>Cosmic Trip创造了至今最直观的VR游戏控制系统，让你彻底沉浸于异星世界。<br><br><strong>惊艳的美术<\/strong><br>曾在2016年度Proto Award与2016 VR Core Award中被提名最佳艺术风格与最佳视觉设计。Cosmic Trip将为您带来五彩缤纷的异星世界与美不胜收的风景。<br><br><strong>真正的VR即时战略<\/strong><br>Cosmic Trip为您带来了真正的浸入式的即时战略模式。在抢先体验玩家们的帮助下，我们得以打造出终极的VR体验！感受自动炮塔轰炸敌人的快感，聆听机器人小伙伴为您播放的动听旋律，然后享受您创造的的机器人大军在咫尺处粉碎外星人军队吧！<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/427240\/extras\/newtest2.jpg?t=1725382268\" \/><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">自抢先体验以来的大型更新：<\/h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>全新游戏模式：<\/strong>自抢先体验版本后，我们新增了3个全新的游戏模式（包括完整的战略模式！）<br><\/li><li><str